### Listar todos los alumnos
GET {{url}}/alumnos
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Buscar alumno por ID
GET {{url}}/alumnos/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Crear alumno
POST {{url}}/alumnos
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nombre": "Esteban",
