}

### Modificar alumno
PUT {{url}}/alumnos/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nombre": "Sandro",
  "apellido": "Mansilla",
  "dni": 98765432
}

### Eliminar alumno
DELETE {{url}}/alumnos/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}